Followers of the Mexico-based Pentecostal church La Luz del Mundo (Light of the World) participate in a baptism ceremony in Guadalajara, Mexico on Sunday. Naason Joaquin Garcia, leader of the controversial church, is imprisoned in the US awaiting trial on charges of rape of minors, among others. Photo: AFP  
